Pac-Man and the Ghostly Adventures - Season 1 - Complete (WEB-DL - 1080p)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

Pac-Man and the Ghostly Adventures follow the daily events of Pac as he saves
PacWorld. Together with his friends Cyli and Spiral, Pac and his buds face the
issues of being teenagers while also protecting PacWorld from a ghostly army led
by evil Lord Betrayus. Thanks to the school bully, Pac-Man accidentally opens the
portal to the Netherworld, unleashing an army of ghosts, led by the fiery Lord
Betrayus! Lucky for Pac-World, the Legend of Last Yellow Orb proves to be true.

Produced by 41 Entertainment, Arad Productions and Namco Bandai Games.
